snippet.title: Jet Set Radio MiniMix:  How To Play
snippet.description:
Yo, are you lost and don't know what to do?  Don't know which buttons do what.  Well sit down and let me show you a few things.

Song Used in Video:  https://soundcloud.com/officiallipsey/hideki-naganuma-brother-goes
Link to Trailer:  https://youtu.be/q5b5zELIxk4

= Download Links =
  Version 1.0d3
    Full Version(390mb):  https://mega.nz/file/qZEixZhL#URkdnb6jSHeSwNeCsAOEvHsMJhDsxrgzD_jfxkaivPI
    Lite Version(70mb):  https://mega.nz/file/HAVACJLY#5iuvU2SZF_27sRO4Fir5oFKXqjMRJrsLpuapNDSKt9s
 *The Full version has JSRL Integration (JSRL Integration may no longer work due to JSRL being updated 3-26-23).
